  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition" corresp="#Ed">
    <body>
      <div type="mūlam" rend="parallel">
        <lg xml:id="TNV16">
        <l>viṉātalum viṭuttaluṅ kaḻaṟalu maṟuttalu</l>
<l>nōtalum yāṇṭeṉa viṉṉuḻi yeṉṟalu</l>
<l>mātaraik kāṇṭalu maṉṉiya vakuttaluṅ</l>
<l>kiḻavōṟ kicaittalu māṟṟāṉ kiḷattalum</l>
<l>paḻavarai viṭuttalum pāṅkaṟ kūṭṭam</l></lg>
<p xml:lang="en">Questioning [the hero], letting out [the secret], reproaching [him], refusing,
[friend’s] suffering, [when asked] ‘Where?’ saying ‘In such a place.’, seeing the woman, 
classifying [her as] agreeable, speaking to the hero, making it clear that he cannot bear and 
sending [her] off to the old ones (i.e. her family) - these are the union [by means of] the friend.
</p>
</div>
</body>
</text>
<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition" corresp="#Ed">
    <body>
      <head xml:lang="en">Commentary</head>
      <p xml:id="TNV16comm1">e-tu. pāṅkaṟ kūṭṭam ām āṟuṇarttutaṉutaliṟṟu.</p>
      <p xml:lang="en">The quoted [<hi rend="italic">cūttiram</hi>] intends to make known the way in which 
      the meeting [by means of the] friend occurs.</p>
    <p xml:id="TNV16comm2">pāṅkaṉ talaimakaṟkuṟṟa viṉātalun talaimakaṉ iṉṉateṉṟalum pāṅkaṉ kaḻaṟalun talaimakaṉ 
    kaḻaṟṟetir maruttalum pāṅkaṉōtalum evviṭattevvuru veṉṟalun talaimakaṉ iṉṉa viṭattu iṉṉa vuru veṉṟalum 
    pāṅkaṉ avviṭattavvuruk kāṇṭalun talaimakaṉaip perumai kūṟalum peyarntu vantu talaimakaṟkuraittalun 
    talaimakaṉ ṟalaimakaḷaik kaṇṭaṇaitalum uṟaviṉ āṟṟāṉ kūṟalum viṭuttalum pāṅkaṟ kūṭṭam ām eṉṟa vāṟu.</p>
<div type="citation" rend="parallel">
        <lg xml:id="TNV16poem1">
<l>muṉṉiṉai muṭippatoṉ ṟuḷatukoṉ mūvakai</l>
<l>nuṇṇiya paṉuvali ṉuḻaintako</l>
<l>leṉṉaikol vāṭiya taṇṇaṉiṉ ṉeḻilē</l>        
</lg></div>
<div type="koḷu" rend="parallel">
<p xml:id="TNV16koḷu1">eṉpatu viṉātal.</p>
</div> 
<div type="citation" rend="parallel">
        <lg xml:id="TNV16poem2">
 <l>ciṟuveḷ ḷaravi ṉavvarik kuruḷai</l>
<l>kāṉa yāṉai yaṇaṅki yāaṅ</l>
<l>kiḷaiyaṇ muḷaivā ḷeyiṟṟaḷ</l>
<l>vaḷaiyuṭaik kaiyaḷem maṇaṅki yōḷē</l>
<trailer>[kuṟun - 119]</trailer>
</lg>
</div>    
<div type="koḷu" rend="parallel">
<p xml:id="TNV16koḷu2">eṉpatu pāṅkaṟkut talaimakaṉ kūṟiyatu.</p>
</div>
 <div type="citation" rend="parallel">
        <lg xml:id="TNV16poem3">
<l>poruntā tamma puṉaiyiḻai yarivai</l>
<l>muruntēr muṟuva ṉōkki</l>
<l>varuntiṉa ṉeṉpatu peruntakai peritē</l>
</lg>
</div>
<div type="koḷu" rend="parallel">
<p xml:id="TNV16koḷu3">eṉpatu pāṅkaṉ kaḻaṟiyatu.</p>
</div>
<div type="citation" rend="parallel">
        <lg xml:id="TNV16poem4">
<l>kāṇkuvi rāyiṟ kaḻaṟalir maṉṉō</l>
<l>pūṇpuṉai vaḷariḷa vaṉamulai</l>
<l>māṇkuḻai mātar maṭaṅkeḻu nōkkē</l>
</lg>
</div>
<div type="koḷu" rend="parallel">
<p xml:id="TNV16koḷu4">eṉpatu kaḻaṟṟetir maṟuttatu.</p>
</div>
<div type="citation" rend="parallel">
        <lg xml:id="TNV16poem5">
<l>pulantuṟai pōkiya neñcuniṟai yaḻintu</l>
<l>kalaṅkuva tāyiṉ mātō</l>
<l>cilampaṉai yārō teḷikkunar piṟarē</l>
</lg>
</div>           
<div type="koḷu" rend="parallel">
<p xml:id="TNV16koḷu5">eṉpatu pāṅkaṉ piḻaittaṉaṉ eṉṟāṟṟāṉāyiṟṟu.</p>
</div>
 <div type="citation" rend="parallel">
        <lg xml:id="TNV16poem6"> 
<l>vāḻvati yāvatu kollō vāṉpukaḻc</l>
<l>cūḻkaḻa laṇṇa ṉeñca</l>
<l>māḻtuya reyta vaṇaṅkiya vaṇaṅkē</l>   
</lg>
</div>
<div type="koḷu" rend="parallel">
<p xml:id="TNV16koḷu6">eṉpatu pāṅkaṉ iṭam viṉāyiṟṟu.</p>
</div>
<div type="citation" rend="parallel">
        <lg xml:id="TNV16poem7">
<l>kaṇṇē kāviyaṅ kayamalar nutalē</l>
<l>taṇṇiḷa matiyeṉat takumē patiyum</l>
<l>perumalaic cāraṟ cīṟū</l>
<l>rarumai vāṅkiya vāyiḻai taṉakkē</l>
</lg>
</div>
<div type="koḷu" rend="parallel">
<p xml:id="TNV16koḷu7">eṉpatu talaimakaṉ kuṟiyuraittatu.</p>
</div>
<div type="citation" rend="parallel">
        <lg xml:id="TNV16poem8">
<l>vēṅkai yoḷvī kāntaḷoṭu kamaḻum</l>
<l>pūntaṇ cāralu mituvē yēntilai</l>
<l>yayilvē laṇṇal kūṟiya</l>
<l>mayilēr cāyal vaṇṇamu mituvē</l>
</lg>
</div>
<div type="koḷu" rend="parallel">
<p xml:id="TNV16koḷu8">eṉpatu pāṅkaṉ etirppaṭṭatu.</p>
</div>
<div type="citation" rend="parallel">
        <lg xml:id="TNV16poem9">
<l>nōtaka vuṭaittē neñca matimicai</l>
<l>mātark kuvaḷai malarmalarn taṉṉa</l>
<l>karuntaṭaṅ kaṇkaṇ ṭāṟṟiyap</l>
<l>peruntakai yaṇṇalaik kaḻaṟiṉaṉ peritē</l>
</lg>
</div>
<div type="koḷu" rend="parallel">
<p xml:id="TNV16koḷu9">eṉpatu talaimakaṉ āṟṟal kūṟiyatu.</p>
</div>
<div type="citation" rend="parallel">
        <lg xml:id="TNV16poem10">
<l>āytaḷir potuḷiya vītatai taṇciṉaik</l>
<l>kāykatir nuḻaiyāk kaṭipoḻil</l>
<l>yāvayi ṉōrum viḻaivuṟun takaittē</l>    
</lg>
</div>
 <div type="koḷu" rend="parallel">
<p xml:id="TNV16koḷu10">eṉpatu pāṅkaṉ peyarntu vantu talaimakaṟ kurai ttatu.</p>
</div>
<div type="citation" rend="parallel">
        <lg xml:id="TNV16poem11">
<l>taṉimai neñcattu muṉivukaṇ ṇakaṟṟaliṉ</l>
<l>viṉaimāṇ pāvai yaṉṉa</l>
<l>puṉaiyiḻai mātarum pōṉṟatip poḻilē</l>
</lg>
</div>
<div type="koḷu" rend="parallel">
<p xml:id="TNV16koḷu11">eṉpatu talaimakaṉ avviṭattuc ceṉṟatu.</p>
</div>
<div type="citation" rend="parallel">
        <lg xml:id="TNV16poem12">
<l>teyva māka vaiyuṟu neñcam</l>
<l>poyyā tāyiṉiṉ cevvāy payanta</l>
<l>kiḷipurai kiḷaviyām peṟuka</l>
<l>voḷiyiḻai maṭantai yuyirpeyarp paritē</l>
</lg>
</div>
<div type="koḷu" rend="parallel">
<p xml:id="TNV16koḷu12">eṉpatu talaimakaṉ aṇaital uṟaviṉ āṟṟāṉ kūṟiyatu.</p>
</div>
<div type="citation" rend="parallel">
        <lg xml:id="TNV16poem13">
<l>kāviyaṅ karuṅkaṭ cevvāyp paintoṭi</l>
<l>pūviri curimeṉ kūntalum</l>
<l>vēypurai tōḷu maṇaṅkumā lemmē</l>
</lg>
</div>
<div type="koḷu" rend="parallel">
<p xml:id="TNV16koḷu13">ituvum atu</p>
</div>
<div type="citation" rend="parallel">
        <lg xml:id="TNV16poem14">
<l>perumalarp pirinta tirumaka ḷammala</l>
<l>raruṅkavi ṉeytac ceṉṟu cērntāṅ</l>
<l>karuṅkalat toṉmaṉai poliyap</l>
<l>peruntakait tōḷi peyarntaṉai ceṉmē</l>
</lg>
</div>
<div type="koḷu" rend="parallel">
<p xml:id="TNV16koḷu14">eṉpatu talaimakaḷai viṭuttal. <note>16.</note></p>
</div>
